            "
            When the product dose not support unisLswCpuUsageRecoverThreshold,
            the trap indicates that the CPU usage decreased to or below
            the unisLswCpuUsageMinorThreshold.
            When the product supports unisLswCpuUsageRecoverThreshold,
            the trap indicates that the CPU usage decreased to or below
